#  ExtraAI — .env Configuration Template
#  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Copy this file to .env and paste your FRESH AI API keys.
#
#  ⚠️ IMPORTANT: The keys you shared in chat were compromised.
#     Generate NEW ones and paste them below.
#
#  STEP-BY-STEP:
#    1. Copy .env.example to .env
#    2. Generate FRESH Groq key: https://console.groq.com/keys
#    3. Generate FRESH Gemini key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#    4. Paste both keys below
#    5. Save file
#
#  NOTE: Chat history user ke phone mein (browser localStorage) save
#  hoti hai. DATABASE_URL ki zaroorat NAHI hai.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── AI KEYS (Both FREE — generate fresh ones) ───

# Groq — Fast text answers
# Get FRESH key: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=PASTE_YOUR_FRESH_GROQ_KEY_HERE

# Google Gemini — Vision + smart answers
# Get FRESH key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=PASTE_YOUR_FRESH_GEMINI_KEY_HERE

# ─── ADMOB (Already configured in src/config/admob.ts) ───
# Aap ki AdMob IDs (app_id, banner, interstitial) already
# src/config/admob.ts mein pre-configured hain. Kuch nahi karna.
